  "detailed_description": "Ever wanted a relaxing game to play while watching movies, or just to distract yourself?<br>Relaxing Lawnmower Simulator is simple, calming game to play when stressed, or while you're watching movies in the background. It features a freeroam mode, where you can freely roam in a wide field of grass to mow, while listening to the sound of distant waves and birds. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192890/extras/58266d93daade740c83862bccf85a239.poster.avif?t=1768827152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192890/extras/58266d93daade740c83862bccf85a239.webm?t=1768827152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192890/extras/58266d93daade740c83862bccf85a239.mp4?t=1768827152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Additionally, you can play the \"Challenge\" mode, where you have to mow various residents lawns in time before they get annoyed at you taking too long.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192890/extras/bbab560d66fcd3ba2641d26124fa824c.poster.avif?t=1768827152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192890/extras/bbab560d66fcd3ba2641d26124fa824c.webm?t=1768827152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192890/extras/bbab560d66fcd3ba2641d26124fa824c.mp4?t=1768827152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
